OL,3,CCouncils warn SEND deficits mean they
OL,4,Ccould go bankrupt 'overnight'
OL,6,FThe County Councils Network says the
OL,7,Fsituation is now "unmanageable", ITV
OL,8,FNews Deputy Political Editor Anushka
OL,9,FAsthana reports
OL,11,FA decision to let English councils
OL,12,Fbuild up "hidden deficits" to cover
OL,13,Fthe surging cost of special
OL,14,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,15,F(SEND) now risks bankrupting almost
OL,16,Fthree-quarters of the largest local
OL,17,Fauthorities, it has been warned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
