OL,3,CCouncils warn SEND deficits mean they
OL,4,Ccould go bankrupt 'overnight'
OL,6,FResearch shared exclusively with ITV
OL,7,FNews and the FT reveals that councils
OL,8,F- which have been allowed to use an
OL,9,Faccounting fudge to keep the losses
OL,10,Foff their balance sheets - have
OL,11,Falready amassed SEND deficits of #4
OL,12,Fbillion nationwide.
OL,14,FThe data - from the County Councils
OL,15,FNetwork (CCN), Society of County
OL,16,FTreasurers and Association of Local
OL,17,FAuthority Treasurers - suggests the
OL,18,Ffigure will balloon to #5.9 billion
OL,19,Fnext year, and then #8 bn after that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
