OL,3,CCouncils warn SEND deficits mean they
OL,4,Ccould go bankrupt 'overnight'
OL,6,FA separate survey of its members by
OL,7,Fthe CCN reveals that 26 councils
OL,8,Fbelieve they will have to trigger a
OL,9,Fsection 114 and effectively declare
OL,10,Fbankruptcy by the end of 2027 if the
OL,11,Ffunding crisis is not fixed. Wiltshire
OL,12,FCouncil is one of 18 councils warning
OL,13,Fit would go insolvent immediately if
OL,14,Fthe override is withdrawn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
