OL,3,CCouncils warn SEND deficits mean they
OL,4,Ccould go bankrupt 'overnight'
OL,6,FIts leader, Councillor Richard Clewer,
OL,7,Fsaid Wiltshire was in a stable
OL,8,Fposition overall but added: "If the
OL,9,Fstatutory override wasn't in place
OL,10,Fthis would dramatically change the
OL,11,Fpicture. With our special educational
OL,12,Fneeds deficit already outstripping all
OL,13,Favailable reserves, we would be
OL,14,Ftechnically bankrupt overnight."
OL,16,FHe said the situation was
OL,17,F"unsustainable" and needed urgent
OL,18,Freform.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
